{"word":"Λητῷος","slug":"Λητῷος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>Λητῷος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:Λητώ'><el>Λητώ</el></a>\n<el>(Λητῷος, η, ον) </el><p/><i>of</i> or <i>born from Leto</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; doric <el>Λατῴα</el>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>: <a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> also <el>Λητωίς, ίδος</el>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}